{"tid":2286164,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中國校友會排名擬似造假 虛假香港大學上榜","createTime":"2020-11-14T17:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T08:19:08.000Z","uid":225931,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4bfa2dc22afe0572e557cd52819b434d8e680183","tid":2286164,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T17:45:25.000Z","msg":"從來都冇聽過依問 香港影視傳媒學院 竟然排名仲高過浸會大學 同QS Top10 嘅香港演藝學院齊名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n番查 香港大專院校列表 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發現根本冇佢個名 啫係野雞學院啦 連大學都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而依個校友會排名係大陸一向幾有公信力 唔排除間野買榜 唔知今次會唔會搞到誠信破產呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VhXBkZk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVhXBkZk.jpg&h=292e399e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79ba583d5c1c8daa72124150ff6e50ebafc49c2d","tid":2286164,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T17:49:26.000Z","msg":"Link:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cuaa.net/paihang/news/news.jsp?information_id=136182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cuaa.net%2Fpaihang%2Fnews%2Fnews.jsp%3Finformation_id%3D136182&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BEBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=c148d6ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cuaa.net/paihang/news/news.jsp?information_id=136182</a>"},{"pid":"c55da710ba04e45fc8130716f7b8a1cd2b910a75","tid":2286164,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T18:06:57.000Z","msg":"校友會排名喺大陸都係比人叫做「野榜」㗎wor，個網都似足典型支那呃人網"},{"pid":"5e710da71f4d99eed8d5ecd7d9c7c83027dff793","tid":2286164,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T18:17:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f21a5c1f6dbc07cef8d11f5010394e2c1a4e3c24","tid":2286164,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"reply